IdImager Photo Supreme

Description: Do you own a digital camera? Then in no time you will have thousands of images on your computer, and finding that one image you are looking for will become a chore. But Photo Supreme can change all that. Whether you have 1,000 or 500,000 images in your archive, Photo Supreme’s integrated photo cataloging and photo management features will help you quickly find and work with your desired image.
Features:

 

    Advanced search capabilities
    Multi Tab Browsing
    Import/Ingest images
    Side-by-Side comparison (up to 6 images)
    Keyword tagging
    Advanced GEO Tagging
    Image organization in portfolios
    Duplicate Detection
    Share images withFlickr, Smugmug, Zenfolio, Picasaweb, FTP, EMail
    Dual Monitor Support
    Creative Commons support
    Face Detection
